{"tid":52437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老喜訊】南港島綫新增關愛𨋢","createTime":"2016-12-24T05:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T10:47:08.000Z","uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9215be788bfe8499c90f6d09edf7ee0c704241","tid":52437,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161224/large/1482555619_e4b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161224%2Flarge%2F1482555619_e4b2.jpg&h=a80fc895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵優先座問題已甚惹爭議，今次南港鐵綫通車，港鐵更新引入「優先𨋢」，車站內前往大堂的電梯全部貼上紅色優先使用貼紙，供有需要人士優先使用。港鐵車務營運總管李聖基指，由於車站有多條扶手梯前往各層，因而考慮引入優先使用電梯方便有需要人士使用。<br />\n<br />\n李聖基又指，金鐘站現有荃灣綫及港島綫月台的擴建位置，今日雖仍落下防火閘及以膠布圍封，主要是因有關位置可通往擴建部分，需要在周三南港島綫通車時同步啟用。他又強調，車站工程經已全部完成，可於通車日全部啟用。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早前南港島綫列車在測試期間曾經死機，李強調列車所有大問題已處理，目前尚餘輕微調較作正進行，如令列車停站更準確。他又指，南港島綫車站始終按中型鐵路規模設計，會密切留意人流問題，各站會有人流管制措施對應。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161224/56087474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161224%2F56087474&d=CLs%2FCSULAZ2phu0cgJ4cPaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=3b1f5f9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161224%2F56087474&h=9a0702ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161224/56087474</a>"},{"pid":"7e182eff502e7d5fbcd6c65948c59b496261a4b1","tid":52437,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ded07ce4291a01ce5a0e0a2ffe2f6fa257ff33","tid":52437,"uid":4043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15cdfd0c6282b318301d1b0c1258ea18a5